{"tid":1921351,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有車牌係咪等於識揸車？","createTime":"2020-03-12T02:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T09:32:23.000Z","uid":5995,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b230235f55c4df93ef47d8c88c32cec59dffa445","tid":1921351,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"公司請送貨 有條友黎見工<br />\n話做開文職最近比人雞左<br />\n想試下其他工 問佢識唔識揸車 佢話識<br />\n考左牌3年 不過冇揸過<br />\n我即刻屌柒佢 咁都叫識揸車？比左架車你咪仆街做馬路炸彈 罵撚到佢頭dupdup咁<br />\n跟住叫佢返屋企算<br />\n<br />\n家陣係有車牌=識揸車？"},{"pid":"610a12450a60d546790024a1c655600ffcc3fd09","tid":1921351,"uid":47230,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"你問佢識唔識咋嘛 佢真係識喎"},{"pid":"e4faddbc6d5f6ba124c323c33fc6574163e7e760","tid":1921351,"uid":180168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"唔識揸車點考車牌<br />\n最多話佢未夠經驗啫"},{"pid":"33f2dff27c4aadbcec940c26b7f070b90ac4a4dc","tid":1921351,"uid":123591,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"唔識點有牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢最多叫新手"},{"pid":"4f48c5d234173f34b270795d76f4ca22ddfb8413","tid":1921351,"uid":217862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610a12450a60d546790024a1c655600ffcc3fd09","tid":1921351,"uid":47230,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:46:22.000Z","msg":"你問佢識唔識咋嘛 佢真係識喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:49:21.000Z","msg":"咪係囉<br />\n佢都係答其所問<br />\n樓豬問佢路面經驗多唔多又另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2f541572e6e5e57795ae45b07060c1858bba5e","tid":1921351,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"識同叻 差好遠既"},{"pid":"fd1987883fb7e5a7f73894fd38d097a12b8bc03f","tid":1921351,"uid":256768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔代表識，因為有人會考張雪藏牌。我九月考到，最近先開始揸返，